Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount email
Host imap.gmail.com
User MY_USER
Pass MY_PWD
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore email-remote
Account email

MaildirStore email-local
Path ~/.mutt/MY_USER/
Inbox ~/.mutt/MY_USER/inbox

Channel email-inbox
Master :email-remote:
Slave :email-local:
Patterns "INBOX"

Channel email-sent
Master :email-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Slave :email-local:sent

Channel email-trash
Master :email-remote:"[Gmail]/Trash"
Slave :email-local:trash

Group email
Channel email-inbox
Channel email-sent
Channel email-trash

